<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4780328>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. A. Habit. B. Cauline node and internode enlargement. C. Leaf apex, showing evenly spaced smooth marginal trichomes. D. Dendritic trichome with terete radiating arms. E. Simple axillary dichasium. F. Flower at anthesis (profile view). G. Elongated trichome with roughened base. H. Petal, showing reflexed posture. I. Stamen (profile view). J. Seeds, dorsal view (lower) and profile view (upper). All drawn from the holotype." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4780328/files/figure.png" .

